  "prompt": "What are some really good Korean spas in Minneapolis?",
  "response": "Minneapolis has a few great options for Korean spas, where you can enjoy traditional treatments and relaxation. Here are a couple of well-regarded ones:\n\n1. **The W Spa** - Known for its authentic Korean spa experience, The W Spa offers a variety of services, including body scrubs, massages, and skin treatments. It features a vibrant, communal atmosphere with saunas, hot tubs, and relaxation areas.\n\n2. **Spa World** - Although it's more of a sauna and relaxation center, Spa World offers a unique experience with various sauna rooms, a hot and cold pool, and massage treatments. It's a great place to unwind!\n\n3. **Healing Touch Spa** - While not exclusively a Korean spa, it offers various Asian-inspired treatments, including traditional body scrubs and massages that may align with what you're looking for.\n\nBefore your visit, it might be a good idea to check their current services and availability, as well as any specific amenities they offer. Enjoy your spa day!",
